    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the S54B32 engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for a linear, high-revving power band. This driver-focused example utilizes a 6-speed manual Getrag gearbox and a 3.64 ratio limited-slip differential. Crucial preventative maintenance is documented, including rear subframe reinforcement, rod bearing replacement, and a recent valve shim adjustment. The chassis is enhanced with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, maintaining the sharp handling and communicative steering feel inherent to the platform. While the exterior shows minor road wear typical of a 'good' condition driver, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity remain exceptional for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
