    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the ideal find for a buyer seeking reliability without the 'new car' price tag. The exterior retains a brilliant gloss, with only the slightest, negligible imperfections consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the interior is remarkably clean; the upholstery is firm and free of stains or odors, and the dashboard remains crack-free with all electronic features\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014functioning perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth, consistent power. It has been strictly maintained with high-quality fluids, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, honest car that has clearly been a point of pride for its previous owner and is ready to provide years of dependable service to its next.",
